“In Apache Spark, approxQuantile computes approximate percentiles of a column efficiently without sorting the entire dataset.”

🧠 First—What is a Quantile?

👉 Quantile = value below which a percentage of data falls

Example dataset:

[10, 20, 30, 40, 50]
0.5 → median → 30
0.25 → 25th percentile → 20
0.75 → 75th percentile → 40

df.approxQuantile("age", [0.25, 0.5, 0.75], 0.01)
